'''尼尔·海伍德'''（{{lang-en|'''Neil Heywood'''}}，中文又译：'''尼尔·伍德'''，粵語又譯：'''尼爾·希活'''，{{bd|1970年|10月20日|2011年|11月14日|Heywood, Neil}}<ref name="tt2">{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/9171996/Chinese-police-chief-sought-UK-meeting-on-businessmans-death.html |title=Chinese police chief sought UK meeting on businessman's death |publisher=每日电讯报 |author=Malcolm Moore |date=2012-03-29 |accessdate=2012-03-29 |archive-date=2012-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120329164438/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/9171996/Chinese-police-chief-sought-UK-meeting-on-businessmans-death.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>），英国公民，其曾外祖父約翰·巴爾·阿弗萊克（John Barr Affleck）于1935至1938年是英國駐天津的總領事<ref>{{cite news| language = zh-hant| url = http://news.wenweipo.com/2014/01/11/IN1401110034.htm| title = 三聯生活周刊記錄:薄瓜瓜在英國| publisher = 文匯網| accessdate = 2014-01-11| archive-date = 2018-11-03| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181103114254/http://news.wenweipo.com/2014/01/11/IN1401110034.htm| dead-url = no}}</ref>。曾担任商业咨询顾问。生前曾长期居住在中国大陆。与前[[中共中央政治局委员|中共中央政治局委员]]、[[重庆市委|重庆市委]]书记[[薄熙来|薄熙来]]一家关系密切。2011年，海伍德与薄熙来妻子[[薄谷开来|薄谷开来]]发生争执后于11月死于重庆市<ref name="telegraph_9201211" />。

==生平==
1970年10月20日，海伍德生于英国西伦敦[[肯辛顿|肯辛顿]]，在[[克拉珀姆|克拉珀姆]]长大。1984年到1988年，海伍德进入[[哈罗公学|哈罗公学]]学习<ref name="ReferenceA"/>。1989年，他进入[[华威大学|华威大学]]主修国际关系学。1992年毕业后曾在英国下议院工作。<ref name="tt1"/><ref name="tt2"/><ref name="tt3">{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/9176227/I-think-Neil-Heywood-was-killed...-everyones-scared.html |title='I think Neil Heywood was killed... everyone’s scared’ |publisher=每日电讯报 |author=Malcolm Moore |date=2012-03-31 |accessdate=2012-04-11 |archive-date=2012-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120401210126/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/9176227/I-think-Neil-Heywood-was-killed...-everyones-scared.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="telegraph_9178179">{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/9178179/Neil-Heywood-feared-for-his-safety-as-strains-grew-around-Bo-Xilai-his-powerful-Chinese-friend.html|title=Neil Heywood 'feared for his safety' as strains grew around Bo Xilai, his powerful Chinese friend|date=2012-03-31|work=每日电讯报|accessdate=2012-04-10|archive-date=2012-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120408212422/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/9178179/Neil-Heywood-feared-for-his-safety-as-strains-grew-around-Bo-Xilai-his-powerful-Chinese-friend.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="tt5">{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/9169808/British-middle-man-found-dead-in-China-and-his-links-to-intelligence-company.html|title=British middle man found dead in China and his links to intelligence company|date=27 Mar 2012|work=每日电讯报|accessdate=14 April 2012|archive-date=2012-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120416144155/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/9169808/British-middle-man-found-dead-in-China-and-his-links-to-intelligence-company.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ibtimes00" />

1990年代初，海伍德前往[[北京语言大学|北京语言大学]]学习[[中文|中文]]<ref name="guardian00">{{cite news|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2012/mar/27/dead-british-businessmen-china-mi6-links|title=Dead British businessman in China had links to ex-MI6 officers' firm|publisher=卫报|date=2012-03-27|accessdate=2012-04-14|archive-date=2012-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120415063219/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2012/mar/27/dead-british-businessmen-china-mi6-links|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ibtimes00">{{cite news|url=http://cn.ibtimes.com/articles/10333/20120412/neil-heywood-sheng-ping-bo-xi-lai.htm|title=英国公民尼尔·伍德生平及与薄熙来一家关系的梳理|publisher=国际财经日报|date=2012-04-12|accessdate=2012-04-12|archive-date=2012-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120413193444/http://cn.ibtimes.com/articles/10333/20120412/neil-heywood-sheng-ping-bo-xi-lai.htm|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。之后，他与朋友克里斯多夫·伯丁顿（Christopher Boddington）在[[大连|大连]]开了一家名为海伍德与伯丁顿联合公司（Heywood Boddington Associates）的顾问咨询公司，以帮助外国公司进入与调研中国市场<ref name="tt3" />。2000年，海伍德在英国注册了一家名为“尼尔·海伍德联合公司”（Neil Heywood & Associates），主要业务为撰写有关亚洲市场的分析文章<ref name="telegraph_9201211">{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/9201211/Neil-Heywood-gave-Bo-Xilais-financial-secrets-to-lawyer-before-his-death.html|title=Neil Heywood 'gave Bo Xilai's financial secrets to lawyer before his death'|publisher=每日电讯报|author=Martin Beckford|date=2012-04-13|accessdate=2012-04-14|archive-date=2012-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120413222800/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/9201211/Neil-Heywood-gave-Bo-Xilais-financial-secrets-to-lawyer-before-his-death.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>及并为《[[经济学人|经济学人]]》杂志撰写文章<ref name="telegraph_9178179" />。

在[[薄熙来|薄熙来]]任大连市长期间，海伍德曾向其致信愿意帮助他吸引外资入大连，从而与薄建立联系<ref name="nyt00">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/04/12/world/asia/bo-xilai-scandal-and-the-mysterious-neil-heywood.html|title=Briton’s Wanderings Led Him to Heart of a Chinese Scandal|author=SHARON LaFRANIERE, JOHN F. BURNS|publisher=纽约时报|date=2012-04-11|accessdate=2012-04-14|archive-date=2012-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120414004856/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/04/12/world/asia/bo-xilai-scandal-and-the-mysterious-neil-heywood.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他也曾任薄熙来的儿子[[薄瓜瓜|薄瓜瓜]]的英语教师，曾为薄瓜瓜在英国留学做过咨询工作，帮助其进入[[哈罗公学|哈罗公学]]<ref name="nyt326">{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/03/27/world/asia/uk-seeks-probe-of-britons-death-in-china.html?ref=china# |title=Britain Seeks Investigation of Businessman’s Death in China |publisher=《纽约时报》 |author=MICHAEL WINES 与 SHARON LaFRANIERE |date=2012-03-26 |accessdate=2012-03-27 |language=en |archive-date=2017-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170111082440/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/03/27/world/asia/uk-seeks-probe-of-britons-death-in-china.html?ref=china |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="voa00">{{cite news|url=http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20120403-uncut-news-145905615.html|title=薄家好友海伍德 “暴死”重庆为哪桩？|author=海涛|publisher=美国之音|date=2012-04-03|accessdate=2012-04-11|archive-date=2012-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120406032532/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20120403-uncut-news-145905615.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。薄熙来2004年被任命为[[中华人民共和国商务部|商务部]]部长后去了北京。海伍德也搬到了北京工作，他生前一直常住北京市郊莱蒙湖[[别墅|别墅]]<ref name="ibtimes00" /><ref name="express00" /><ref name="nyt00" />。

海伍德生前是[[阿斯顿·马丁|阿斯顿·马丁]]汽车公司在北京一家销售公司董事会的非执行董事，他也曾为[[劳斯莱斯|劳斯莱斯]]公司工作过<ref name="au1">{{cite news|url=http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/world/british-fixers-murky-death-linked-to-fallen-leaders-wife/story-fnb64oi6-1226315844589|title=British fixer Neil Heywood's murky death linked to fallen leader Bo Xilai's wife|date=2012-04-02|work=The Australian|accessdate=2012-04-10|archive-date=2012-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120410141853/http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/world/british-fixers-murky-death-linked-to-fallen-leaders-wife/story-fnb64oi6-1226315844589|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="hurun">{{cite web|url=http://www.hurun.net/zhcn/ActivitiesShow.aspx?nid=10|title=HuRun Report — hurun.net|date=|work=hurun.net|accessdate=2012-04-11|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120328171734/http://www.hurun.net/zhcn/ActivitiesShow.aspx?nid=10|archivedate=2012-03-28}}</ref><ref name="bbc00">{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/chinese_news/2012/03/120327_guardian_heywood.shtml|title=英媒深挖薄熙来家同英籍友人的关系|date=2012-03-27|work=BBC中文|accessdate=2012-04-11|archive-date=2012-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120401052836/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/chinese_news/2012/03/120327_guardian_heywood.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。海伍德曾为[[哈克路特公司|哈克路特公司]]提供过服务，哈克路特公司是一家咨询公司，由一位前英国[[军情六处|军情六处]]特工与他人创办，因而有传闻称海伍德为军情六处特工，但海伍德朋友、哈克路特公司、英国情报部门均表示否认，其死后英国政府发言人也称其近期并未为英国政府工作<ref name="ibtimes00" /><ref name="tt3" />。尽管英国政府通常拒绝对相关事件发表评论，英国外交大臣黑格仍然罕见地出面对此予以否认<ref>Branigan, Tania. "[http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2012/apr/26/neil-heywood-mi6-william-hague Murdered Briton Neil Heywood was not employed by MI6, says William Hague] {{Wayback|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2012/apr/26/neil-heywood-mi6-william-hague |date=20120524163056 }}", ''[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]'', April 2012</ref>。《[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]》之后报道称，在采访了英国相关官员后，他们确认尽管不是军情六处的雇员，自2009年起，海伍德定期向军情六处提供情报<ref name=wsj-20121105>{{cite news |url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052970204846304578090740894694144.html |title=Briton Killed in China Had Spy Links |author=Jeremy Page |newspaper=Wall Street Journal |date=5 November 2012 |accessdate=6 November 2012 |archive-date=2012-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121115192446/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052970204846304578090740894694144.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=bbc-20121106>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-china-20216757 |title=Neil Heywood: Briton killed in China 'had spy links' |publisher=BBC |date=6 November 2012 |accessdate=6 November 2012 |archive-date=2012-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121115131427/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-china-20216757 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

海伍德总共在中国生活了近二十年，會说[[普通话|普通话]]。他拥有一辆二手灰色[[捷豹|捷豹]]，由于是一个[[007|007]]迷，他将自己的车牌号为选为“N007W3”<ref name=tg420/>。

==死亡==
[[File:Voa_chinese_lijing_main_building_23Apr12_300.jpg|thumb]]
{{Main|海伍德死亡案}}
<!-- 此处是总结，更多内容请在[[海伍德死亡案|海伍德死亡案]]中撰写 -->
2010年，海伍德拒绝了[[谷开来|谷开来]]要求其离婚并发誓效忠薄家的要求，从而激怒了谷开来。此后，在来自薄家“不可承受的压力”之下，海伍德吸烟加剧并开始脱发，增加体重，还打算离开中国。2011年11月13日，海伍德在[[张晓军_(1979年)|张晓军]]的陪同下被紧急召集前往重庆<ref>{{cite news  |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/9214753/Bo-Xilai-responsible-for-two-more-deaths.html  |title=Bo Xilai 'responsible for two more deaths'  |publisher=每日电讯报  |author=Malcolm Moore  |date=2012-04-19  |accessdate=2012-04-20  |language=en  |archive-date=2012-04-19  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120419214031/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/9214753/Bo-Xilai-responsible-for-two-more-deaths.html  |dead-url=no  }}</ref><ref name=tg420>{{cite news |url= http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/9215943/Neil-Heywood-had-financial-difficulties-in-China.html |title= Neil Heywood 'had financial difficulties in China' |publisher= 每日电讯报 |author=  |date= 2012-04-20 |accessdate= 2012-04-20 |language= en |archive-date= 2012-04-20 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120420140916/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/9215943/Neil-Heywood-had-financial-difficulties-in-China.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。此前，海伍德曾对其朋友称自己“惹上麻烦了”，并已经把薄家在海外投资的相关文件交给了他在英国的律师，作为防止自己发生不测的“保险单”。在飞往重庆后，海伍德未能电话联系到相关联系人，而只能在[[重庆南山丽景度假酒店|重庆南山丽景度假酒店]]内继续等待<ref name=tt4>{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/9199144/Bo-Xilai-Neil-Heywood-stashed-Bos-financial-secrets-with-British-lawyer-as-insurance-policy-before-death.html |title=Bo Xilai: Neil Heywood 'stashed Bo's financial secrets with British lawyer as insurance policy before death' |publisher=每日电讯报 |author=Matthew Holehouse |date=2012-04-12 |accessdate=2012-04-14 |archive-date=2012-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120413222809/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/9199144/Bo-Xilai-Neil-Heywood-stashed-Bos-financial-secrets-with-British-lawyer-as-insurance-policy-before-death.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。谷开来曾请求海伍德帮助其向海外转移资金，但是由于海伍德出价过高未得到谷开来同意，据此海伍德威胁将停止参与并将相关内容曝光<ref name=rt>{{cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/04/16/us-china-leader-murder-idUSBRE83F09620120416 |title=Exclusive: Briton killed after threat to expose Chinese leader's wife: sources |publisher=路透社 |author=Chris Buckley |date=2012-04-16 |accessdate=2012-04-18 |archive-date=2012-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120417222242/http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/04/16/us-china-leader-murder-idUSBRE83F09620120416 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]称，[[王立军|王立军]]告诉美国领事馆官员，2011年11月14日，在谷开来在场的情况下，海伍德在重庆[[重庆南山丽景度假酒店|南山丽景度假酒店]]一房间内被人按倒强行灌入[[氰化物|氰化物]]，起初海伍德将氰化物吐出，随后再次被强行灌入更多的氰化物后死亡<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/9224598/Bo-Xilais-wife-was-in-the-room-when-Neil-Heywood-was-poisoned.html|title=Bo Xilai's wife 'was in the room when Neil Heywood was poisoned' （独家报道）|publisher=每日电讯报|author=Damien McElroy与Malcolm Moore|date=2012-04-24|accessdate=2012-04-25|archive-date=2012-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120424223831/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/9224598/Bo-Xilais-wife-was-in-the-room-when-Neil-Heywood-was-poisoned.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。事发后，该酒店所有工作人员被撤换<ref name=tt6>{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/9207419/Neil-Heywood-death-the-hotel-where-British-businessman-died-in-China.html |title=Neil Heywood death: the hotel where British businessman died in China |publisher=每日电讯报 |author=Malcolm Moore |date=2012-04-16 |accessdate=2012-04-18 |archive-date=2012-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120416230026/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/9207419/Neil-Heywood-death-the-hotel-where-British-businessman-died-in-China.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，重庆官方称其死因为“[[酒精中毒|饮酒过量]]”。11月18日，在未进行[[尸检|尸检]]的情况下海伍德的尸体被[[火化|火化]]，骨灰随后被空运回[[伦敦|伦敦]]<ref name=tg420/>。重庆公安局长[[王立军|王立军]]调查此案期间被薄熙来调任，后前往美国驻成都总领事馆避难，引发[[王立军事件|王立军事件]]。事件后薄熙来、王立军被中央去职，海伍德一案被重新调查，调查认为海伍德死于他杀，薄熙来妻子谷开来和薄家勤务人员[[张晓军_(1979年)|张晓军]]有重大嫌疑，之后谷开来和张晓军皆被捕入狱并在2012年8月被分别判处[[死刑缓期执行|死刑缓期执行]]和有期徒刑9年。谷開來先是同當時的重慶市公安局長[[王立军|王立軍]]商量，準備誣陷海伍德販毒，然後讓王立軍在緝毒抓捕時將海伍德擊斃。<ref>{{Cite web|title=BBC中文網 - 兩岸三地 - 紐約時報：瞥見紅色家族陰暗的一角|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/mobile/chinese_news/2012/08/120810_nytimes_gukailai.shtml|accessdate=2020-08-29|work=www.bbc.com}}</ref>

==家庭==
在大连时期，海伍德认识了一位当地女子王露露（音译）并与其结婚，育有一个女儿奥利维娅（Olivia）和一个儿子彼得（Peter；也有说叫乔治，George），搬去北京后两个孩子在北京德威学院学校（即英国{{le|德威学院|Dulwich College}}的北京分部）上学。<ref name="tt1">{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/9166700/Britain-asks-China-to-probe-death-of-UK-citizen-in-Bo-Xilais-Chongqing.html |title=Britain asks China to probe death of UK citizen in Bo Xilai's Chongqing |publisher=每日电讯报 |author=Malcolm Moore |date=2012-03-26 |accessdate=2012-03-29 |archive-date=2012-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120329021008/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/9166700/Britain-asks-China-to-probe-death-of-UK-citizen-in-Bo-Xilais-Chongqing.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="au1" /><ref name="express00">{{cite news|url=http://www.express.co.uk/posts/view/313184/Who-killed-the-charmer-|title=WHO KILLED THE CHARMER?|publisher=express.co.uk|author=Anna Pukas|date=2012-04-07|accessdate=2012-04-11|archive-date=2012-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120411065811/http://www.express.co.uk/posts/view/313184/Who-killed-the-charmer-/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="nyt00" />

海伍德被害后，王露露曾试图离开中国前往英国，但被中国政府以危害国家安全为由拒绝其出境。

